\section{Preface}

This BLDC ESC is to be used in Shell's Eco-Marathon for the University of
Western Austalia's running team in 2015, \textit{EnVe}. The
\href{http://www.shell.com/global/environment-society/ecomarathon.html}{Shell
Eco-Marathon} challenges students from around the world to design, build and
test ultra energy efficient vehicles.
